        <abstract>
            <p>CD has "for many years been working on the perplexed subject of the origin of varieties &amp; species".</p>
            <p>Asks CAM if he can help procure skins of domestic pigeons, poultry, ducks, and rabbits from Persia. Gives general instructions for anyone he might employ to obtain skins.</p>
            <p>CD would also welcome descriptions of the larger, native quadrupeds.</p>
        </abstract>
